N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 65.1 - Definitions

State Regulations

For the purposes of this Part, the following definitions
apply: (a) Cat means any member of the
species Felis catus, regardless of age, sex or breed. (b) Dog means any member of the species Canis
familiaris, regardless of age, sex or breed. (c) Health certificate means a certificate
issued and signed by a veterinarian, legally qualified to practice in the state
or country of origin. Notes
